{"tid":1088627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川山火 30搜救人員罹難","createTime":"2019-04-02T07:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:45:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b184f9bada51ffbec7cc7fffd171914532861916","tid":1088627,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190402/20647272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F20647272&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6%2BjOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=5a927323\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F20647272&h=bb2ca99c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190402/20647272</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四川山火 30搜救人員罹難<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190402/large/02ch105p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190402%2Flarge%2F02ch105p.jpg&h=2999b212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四川山火因風力突變引起爆燃，30名救援人員遇難。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n四川涼山州木里縣特大山火連續燒了三日兩夜，昨日雖大致被熄滅，但傳來驚人噩耗，有份搜救的30名人員罹難，包括27名消防員及當地林業局局長。習近平、李克強分別對事件批示；涉事的木里縣今年2月才被四川省列出九大山火隱患，官方坦承「專業撲火隊力量不足」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雷電擊中觸發山火<br />\n<br />\n上址原始森林上月30日疑被雷電擊中觸發山火，當局31日派出689名消防員及地方撲火隊員救災。官方指森林地形複雜、坡陡谷深，交通通訊不便，救援難度極高。搜救人員事發時完成部份灌救，前往另一地方途中風向突轉變，火勢再次增強，山林出現「回燃」（在缺氧燃燒時大量新鮮空氣衝入現場觸發爆炸）情況，形成極大火球，搜救隊成員全部失蹤，昨晚更證實全部罹難。<br />\n<br />\n官方公佈，死難者有27名當地消防員，另外有3人屬於地方撲火隊，包括木里縣林業局局長楊達瓦和下屬企業工作人員周平。國家主席習近平及總理李克強均已作出批示，四川省委書記彭清華要求全力以赴做好搜救、滅火、善後和安全防範工作。今次發生山火的木里縣今年二月曾被勒令整改防火措施，當局曾列出縣內九大山火隱患，包括專業撲火隊伍建設不規範等。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞/封面新聞  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n恐炒熱六四氣氛 京下令淡化事件"},{"pid":"5cfecb33e43434bb95d83f8405bf86c026ee68ab","tid":1088627,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"669681b8cb6b2d889a0f75d1b293496248916a6d","tid":1088627,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"又係四川"},{"pid":"74ea038681f41c62ffa4967bd76ac7f2e16266de","tid":1088627,"uid":65504,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有份搜救的30名人員罹難，包括27名消防員及當地林業局局長。習近平、李克強</span>分別對事件批示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc8c97505b2b74d3e5a0f95440c84a2da265a43","tid":1088627,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"當局31日派出<span style=\"color: red;\">689</span>名消防員及地方撲火隊員救災"},{"pid":"4256bebc9e6a6451d68a74aca42c4571683ac376","tid":1088627,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7f4d047a115f787c06cd2829ef0675689121e5","tid":1088627,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74ea038681f41c62ffa4967bd76ac7f2e16266de","tid":1088627,"uid":65504,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有份搜救的30名人員罹難，包括27名消防員及當地林業局局長。習近平、李克強</span>分別對事件批示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"我都係咁睇，剛剛好30個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9324cabadaece85e5289dc1c4dc1c9f142a2cb2","tid":1088627,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"恐炒熱六四氣氛 京下令淡化事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0a869509f1a1240c4b69d0c8c556fe785f495a","tid":1088